{"tid":1035162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中央藉慘案修例 意在全面掌控港","createTime":"2019-02-24T12:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T05:50:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc0d535591979216131ed35ed547f1f60fd7729","tid":1035162,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:31:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190224/20619530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190224%2F20619530&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=e339d010\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190224%2F20619530&h=61aaed35\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190224/20619530</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央藉慘案修例 意在全面掌控港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190224/large/0219gary1003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F0219gary1003.jpg&h=1c77e06c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涂謹申<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】中央透過釋法DQ議員並要求實施《國歌法》後，更借題發揮修訂《逃犯條例》，政界相信中央意圖貫徹對港的全面管治權。特區政府至今迴避中央在此事的角色，但全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳曾指修例「肯定有中央在背後支持才成事」，中聯辦主任王志民更公開警告香港不應成為國家安全「法外之地」，可見北京參與度極高；無論修例建議由中央提出、抑或特區政府主動獻媚，民主黨涂謹申認為修例若獲通過，特首林鄭應辭職明志。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：湯家驊：外籍法官不會被京「買起」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190224/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190224%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=e4f5c48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭助紂為虐<br />\n<br />\n保安局突然建議修訂《逃犯條例》以單次個案式移交逃犯，涵蓋地方除台灣也包括中國及澳門，巧合的是民建聯同日立即與在台被殺少女的家屬見記者，支持修例討回公道，令外界質疑時機巧合，民主派議員朱凱廸等曾質疑港府與民建聯打龍通，藉慘案順水推舟打開司法缺口；政府一直以「堵塞漏洞」為由推動修例，卻拒設「日落條款」僅限處理此單一個案，連資深大律師梁家傑也質疑動機何在？<br />\n<br />\n根據最新的世界正義工程法治指數，已與香港簽訂移交協議的國家不少排名極前，如芬蘭排第3、荷蘭排第5、香港則排16，但建議修例涵蓋的中國只排名75。<br />\n<br />\n中、港兩地商議廿年都未能就移交協議達成共識，無非是因涉及公平審訊等大原則不能妥協，但政府突然建議修例，涂謹申直言對林鄭很失望，「23條起碼喺香港做（本地立法規管本地行為），呢樣嘢（修例）一做咗，我只能夠講佢（林鄭）做呢樣衰嘢，我百分之百不原諒；如果上面逼佢，當然即係話佢冇呢個guts話辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n湯家驊：外籍法官不會被京「買起」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n民主黨擬派逾百人出戰區選<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：外籍法官不會被京「買起」<br />\n修例自毀長城 本地轉機可被移交涂謹申：港人隨時變孟晚舟"},{"pid":"835300969e91e07120d6139307ee1bcc88e32706","tid":1035162,"uid":51620,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借呢單寶島殺人事件嚟開放最後一道門<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制 挑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf85628f99c15bc27a775997739669d679fadd84","tid":1035162,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N7CCMtXzBiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN7CCMtXzBiY&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=a09a4218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N7CCMtXzBiY</a>"},{"pid":"5bdb7da279ca6d515185c6b45609346f6625b104","tid":1035162,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc95e51f41a15dca41755dee776a75dc7296a982","tid":1035162,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"除咗革命仲有咩餘地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe134e9270c8587c81a6639475e9c243993ad176","tid":1035162,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf85628f99c15bc27a775997739669d679fadd84","tid":1035162,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N7CCMtXzBiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN7CCMtXzBiY&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=a09a4218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N7CCMtXzBiY</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"係人都知, 但無人理咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be3e6f8c1cc1a75f37a57ccaa2b48e88ffc6a46","tid":1035162,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807401dd3827dfbfc646dfbeb9d6b6e84023ec25","tid":1035162,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83c14e175091d64d5823ed1fe403fa1e3407615","tid":1035162,"uid":134979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"民主黨涂謹申認為修例若獲通過，特首林鄭應辭職明志。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}